description:
Tap Tap is an app that facilitates the management of the game collection, and keep track of all the games you are interested in.

MAIN FEATURES :

- Collection: All the games, digital or physical that you have in your collection are stored in this list;

- Wishlist: All the games that you still don't have in your collection but want to have stored in this list;

- Profile: you can store the games that you played at least one time, the games that you’re currently playing and the games that you already completed. You can also access the settings and the hero's journey in this view;

— Settings: you can change your name, see which is your favorite platform (based on the amount of games you added to that platform) and see a resume of the amount of the games in each list;

— Hero's Journey: you can unlock some badges by adding games to your collection list. When you tap on the badge symbol next to your name, you will be able to see all the unlocked and locked badges.

For any suggestion contact us by email at support@taptap.io
